      "content": "ugh my head just killed me. like literally felt like a bolt of lightning hit my brain for a sec. it's kinda fading now but i feel super foggy and weird. i probably just didnt drink enough water today lol. should i just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off or is that bad?",
